dataIdInfo.idAbs: This point data layer represents addresses for Dunn County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Dunn_Addresses_2017.
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This layer for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. [Point feature class containing address points issued within Dunn County, WI by the County, City, or Villages. Address points are located within the boundary of the parcel the address was issue for, not access point. Revised 03/22/2017. For questions regarding this dataset, please contact the Dunn County Land Information Office at 715-231-6545 or at lis@co.dunn.wi.us. ]
